The mathematic algorithm for zigzag is:

* originalDiff = numRows * 2 - 2;
* If -&gt; &#39;currRow&#39; equals First or last lines
	* use the originalDiff (numRows * 2 - 2)
* Else -&gt;
	* For each new line:
		 * upperDiff += 2, 
		 * lowerDiff -=2	
	
